"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"125\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"tc_sub f_pron\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 3px; color: #a0a0a0; font-family: \'lucida sans unicode\', sans-serif; word-break: break-all !important; float: left;\">B&ugrave;, y&igrave;diǎnr yě b&ugrave; zhīd&agrave;o.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td class=\"ab\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 0px 4px; font-size: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" align=\"right\" width=\"125\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Jim</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"con u\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; text-decoration: underline; float: left; font-size: 15px;\">不，一点儿也不知道。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"125\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"tc_sub\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #a0a0a0; float: left;\">No, not a thing.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"conver_list\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; width: 685px;\">\r\n<table class=\"txt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 685px; word-break: break-all; table-layout: fixed; word-wrap: break-word;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"125\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"tc_sub f_pron\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 3px; color: #a0a0a0; font-family: \'lucida sans unicode\', sans-serif; word-break: break-all !important; float: left;\">C&oacute;ng hāf&oacute; b&igrave;y&egrave; h&ograve;u, tā ji&ugrave; y&igrave;zh&iacute; z&agrave;i zh&egrave;lǐ gōngzu&ograve;, dōu sh&iacute;ni&aacute;n le.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td class=\"ab\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 0px 4px; font-size: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" align=\"right\" width=\"125\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Jack</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"con u\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; text-decoration: underline; float: left; font-size: 15px;\">从哈佛毕业后，他就一直在这里工作，都十年了。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"125\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"tc_sub\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #a0a0a0; float: left;\">He has been working here since his graduation from Harvard University ten years ago.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"conver_list\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; width: 685px;\">\r\n<table class=\"txt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 685px; word-break: break-all; table-layout: fixed; word-wrap: break-word;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"125\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<p class=\"tc_sub f_pron\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 3px; color: #a0a0a0; font-family: \'lucida sans unicode\', sans-serif; word-break: break-all !important; float: left;\">Wā!</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<td class=\"ab\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 0px 4px; font-size: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\" align=\"right\" width=\"125\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Jim</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, simsun; overflow: hidden;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', 'quote', '', 'http://www.nciku.com/conversation/listview?place=office&topic=working%20%20together&by=topic&categoryLanguage=en', '', '1', 'en_SG', '', 'admin', 'admin', '2012-09-13 02:14:20', '2012-09-13 02:14:20', '0');
INSERT INTO cm_article VALUES ('4028d98139c7796a0139c8f90ccc0254', 'Java01', 'Java概述', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">一、简介</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">Java是印度尼西亚</span><a style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/48414.htm\" target=\"_blank\">爪哇岛</a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">的英文名称，因盛产咖啡而闻名。</span><a style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/229611.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Java语言</a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">中的许多库类名称，多与咖啡有关：如JavaBeans（</span><a style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/8402.htm\" target=\"_blank\">咖啡豆</a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">）、NetBeans（网络豆）以及ObjectBeans (</span><a style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/2387.htm\" target=\"_blank\">对象</a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">豆）等等。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;SUN和JAVA的标识也正是一杯正冒着热气的咖啡。</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">Sun Microsystems</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">公司于</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">1995</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">年</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">5</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">月推出,&nbsp;1996年1月第一个JDK-JDK1.0诞生, 1999年6月发布Java的三个版本,2002年2月J2SE1.4发布, 2004年9月J2SE1.5发布</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">更名为Java SE 5.0,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">2006年12月发布JRE6.0,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">2009年04月<strong>甲骨文74亿</strong>美元收购Sun,&nbsp;2010年4月Java之父<strong>JamesGosling</strong>离开Oracle,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">2011年7月发布java7的正式版。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Java是一种跨平台应用软件的面向对象的程序设计语言，是由Java程序设计语言和</span><a style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/209634.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Java平台</a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">（即JavaSE, JavaEE, JavaME）的总称。Java 技术具有卓越的<strong>通用性</strong>、<strong>高效性</strong>、<strong>平台移植性</strong>和<strong>安全性</strong>，广泛应用于个人PC、数据中心、游戏控制台、科学超级计算机、移动电话和互联网。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Java平台由Java<strong>虚拟机</strong>（Java Virtual Machine，简称JVM）和Java <strong>应用编程接口</strong>（Application Programming Interface，简称API）构成。Java 应用编程接口为Java应用提供了一个独立于操作系统的标准接口，可分为基本部分和扩展部分。Java程序可以只编译一次，就可以在各种系统中运行。</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"spctrl\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;<span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Java分为三个体系<strong>JavaSE</strong>(Java2 Platform Standard Edition，java平台标准版)，JavaEE(Java 2 Platform,Enterprise Edition，java平台企业版)，JavaME(Java 2 Platform Micro Edition，java平台微型版)。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"spctrl\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\"><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">二、版本</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">1、J2SE 1.X</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">(1)</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">V1.1.4 Sparkler 宝石 1997-09-12&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">V1.1.5 Pumpkin 南瓜 1997-12-13&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">(3)V1.1.6 Abigail 阿比盖尔--女子名 1998-04-24&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(4)V1.1.7 Brutus 布鲁图--古罗马政治家和将军 1998-09-28&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">(5)V1.1.8 Chelsea 切尔西--城市名 1999-04-08</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">2、J2SE 2.X</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(1)V1.2 Playground 运动场 1998-12-04&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2)V1.2.1 none 无 1999-03-30&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(3)V1.2.2 Cricket 蟋蟀 1999-07-08</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">3、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">J2SE 3.X</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(1)1.3 Kestrel 美洲红隼 2000-05-08&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2)J2SE 1.3.1 Ladybird 瓢虫 2001-05-17</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">4、J2SE 4.X</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(1)V1.4.0 Merlin 灰背隼 2002-02-13&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2)V1.4.1 grasshopper 蚱蜢 2002-09-16&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(3)V1.4.2 Mantis 螳螂 2003-06-26</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">5、Java SE 5.X</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (1)V5.0 Tiger 老虎&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (2)V5.1Dragonfly 蜻蜓&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">(3)</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">新增功能</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; a.泛型: List myIntList = new LinkedList();&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; b.枚举类型: enum Season{winter,spring,summer,fall}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; c.自动打包解包技术: Integer obj1; int num1=69; obj1=num1;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; d.可变长的参数列表: public double average(int...list)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; e.改进的for循环:for(Book myBook:BookList)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; f.annotation定义</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; g.静态的import</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">6、Java SE 6.X</span></strong> </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (1)</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">v6.0 Mustang 野马&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (2)</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">新增功能</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">a.</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">Scanner类为提供了许多读取不同类型数据的便捷方法</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; b.</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">新增</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">printf方法: System.out.printf(\"ID: %5d\\tName: %s\",id,name);</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">c.Instrumentation新功能:类定义动态改变和操作</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">d.</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">Http增强</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; e.JMX与系统管理</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; f.编译器API</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; g.Java DB 与 JDBC4.0</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; h.对脚本语言的支持</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; i.XML API与Web Service</span></p>', '甘剑平', '', '', '', '1', 'zh_CN', '', 'manager', 'manager', '2012-09-15 16:08:48', '2012-09-15 19:51:23', '0');
INSERT INTO cm_article VALUES ('4028d98139c7796a0139c92b14a7028a', 'Java02', 'Java环境', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一、</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">设置环境变量</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">右击&ldquo;我的电脑&rdquo;，选择属性。在系统属性中打开高级选项，点击\"环境变量\"，</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">在&ldquo;用户变量&rdquo;或&ldquo;系统变量&rdquo;中</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.增加系统变量<strong>JAVA_HOME</strong>，值为d:\\program\\j2ee\\jdk15</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2.在现有的<strong>path</strong>环境变量后追加下面的字符串：%JAVA_HOME %\\bin;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3.增加系统变量<strong>CLASSPATH</strong>，其值是：C:\\jdk14\\lib\\tools.jar;C:\\jdk14\\lib\\dt.jar</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4、变量名：JAVA_OPTS &nbsp; 变量值：-Xms256m &nbsp; -Xmx512m</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1G内存的实例:JAVA_OPTS=&rdquo; -Xms800m &ndash;Xmx800m &ndash;XX:PermSize=64M&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&ndash;XX:MaxNexSize=256m &ndash;XX:MaxPermSize=128m&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">二、</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">常用命令</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1、查看jdk版本： <strong>java</strong> <strong>-version</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2、编译：<strong>javac</strong> -classpath common.jar test.java</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3、打jar/war包: &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>jar</strong> <strong>-cvf</strong> jspSource.jar *</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 解压jar/war包: <strong>jar -xvf</strong> jpw.war *</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3、</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">将中文字符的资源文件转换为unicode编码:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">ative2ascci [-reverse] [-encoding utf-8] [输入文件 [输出文件]]</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如: <strong>native2ascci</strong> d:\\resource_zh_CN.properties</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>三、虚拟机加载类机制</strong>：</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">虚拟机在运行一个类时，需要将其装入内存，虚拟机搜索类的方式和顺序如下：</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Bootstrap classes，Extension classes，User classes。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1、Bootstrap 中的路径是虚拟机自带的jar或zip文件，虚拟机首先搜索这些包文件，用System.getProperty(\"<strong>sun.boot.class.path</strong>\")可得到虚拟机搜索的包名。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2、Extension是位于jre\"lib\"ext目录下的jar文件，虚拟机在搜索完Bootstrap后就搜索该目录下的jar文件。用System. getProperty(\"<strong>java.ext.dirs</strong>&rdquo;)可得到虚拟机使用Extension搜索路径。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3、User classes搜索顺序为当前目录、环境变量 CLASSPATH。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">四、Java的内存模型</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.Java的内存模型JMM（Java Memory Model）JMM主要是为了规定了线程和内存之间的一些关系。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2.根据JMM的设计，系统存在一个主内存(Main Memory)，Java中所有实例变量都储存在主存中，对于所有线程都是共享的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3.每条线程都有自己的工作内存(Working Memory)，工作内存由缓存和堆栈两部分组成， 缓存中保存的是主存中变量的拷贝，缓存可能并不总和主存同步。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.堆栈中保存的是线程的局部变量，线程之间无法相互直接访问堆栈中的变量。</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">五、</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Java内存机制</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1、Java把内存划分成两种：一种是<strong>栈内存</strong>，一种是<strong>堆内存</strong>。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(1)在函数中定义的一些基本类型的变量和对象的引用变量都在函数的栈内存中分配。</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">当超过变量的作用域后，Java会自动释放掉为该变量所分配的内存空间，该内存空间可以立即被另作他用，栈式存储分配按照先进后出的原则进行分配。栈主要是用来执行程序的。</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">堆中的内存可以按照任意顺序分配和释放.</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">堆主要用来存放对象的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2)堆内存用来存放由new创建的对象和数组。</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">在堆中分配的内存，由Java虚拟机的自动垃圾回收器来管理。</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">引用变量就相当于是为数组或对象起的一个名称，以后就可以在程序中使用栈中的引用变量来访问堆中的数组或对象。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2、堆heap又分为三个域：新域,旧域generation,永久域Perm</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;java -Xms512m -Xmx512m -Xmn128m</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;-Xmx -Xms 设置JAVA 堆内存的最大值和最小值,设为相同值,默认物理内存的1/64和1/4</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;-XX:PermSize以及-XX:MaxPermSize进行本地内存大小的修改</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;-XX:NewSize和-XX:MaxNewsize设置新域的初始值和最大值 -Xmn新域的大小</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 永久域主要是被JVM存放Class和Meta信息的,GC不会在主程序运行期清理。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">注意:错误常出现在web服务器对JSP进行预编译时,永久域不够。如果WEB-APP下都用大量的第三方jar,超过默认大小(4M),就会报错。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3、</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">按照编译原理的观点,程序运行时的内存分配有三种策略,分别是静态的,栈式的,和堆式的.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 静态存储分配是指在编译时就能确定每个数据目标在运行时刻的存储空间需求,因而在编译时就可以给他们分配固定的内存空间.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></span></p>', '甘剑平', '', '', '', '2', 'zh_CN', '', 'manager', 'manager', '2012-09-15 17:03:27', '2012-09-15 20:09:58', '0');
INSERT INTO cm_article VALUES ('4028d98139c7796a0139c9fdf3d702d8', 'Java03', 'Java基础语法', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">一、基本知识</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; 1、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Java的单词符号有五种：关键字、标识符、常量、分隔符和操作符。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; 2、</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Java标识符必须以字母，数字，美元符号\"$\"，下划线\"_\"组成，标识符第一个字符不可用数字, 区分大小写。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; 3、Java 语言可使用转义字符\'\\\'来标记特殊字符。如\'\\n\'表示换行符，\\\' 表示单引号, &nbsp;\\\\表示反斜杠&ldquo;\\&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; 4、Java的注释有三种形式：<strong>//</strong>Comment, &nbsp;<strong>/**</strong>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Comment&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">*/, &nbsp;/*&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Comment</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;*/&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; 5、</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>算术</strong>运算符：+, -, *, /, %, ++, --. &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>赋值</strong>运算符: +=, -=, *=, /=, %=. &nbsp;<strong>比较</strong>运算符: &gt;, &lt; , &lt;=, &gt;=, !=, ==, instanceof. &nbsp;<strong>逻辑</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">运算符: &amp;(无论任何情况，&ldquo;&amp;&rdquo;两边的表达式都会参与计算), |, !, ^(异或), &amp;&amp;, || &nbsp; <strong>位</strong>运算符：</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&amp;(位与),&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">|(位或),&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">^ 位异或,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&lt;&lt; 左移，左移n位相当于乘以2的n次方,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&gt;&gt; 右移，右移n位相当于除以2的n次,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; 无符号右移.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">二、基本数据类型</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Java不是纯的面向对象的语言, 不纯的地方就是这些基本数据类型不是对象, </span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">这是出于执行效率的权衡。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;1、存储空间。<strong>byte</strong> 8位，<strong>short</strong> 16位，<strong>int</strong> 32位，<strong>long</strong> 64位，<strong>float</strong>32位，<strong>double</strong>64位。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">2、<strong>char</strong>是16位Unicode字符或者说是16位无符号整数，范围从0到65535。可以强制转换非法的数据，如：char c1 = (char) -100。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;3、整数有八进制（以0开头的整数）、十进制、十六进制（以0x或0X开头的整数）表示。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;4、char可以用单引号表示单个字符，如：\'良\'。也可以用unicode值\'\"ucafe\'（四位十六进制数）。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;5、布尔型<strong>boolean</strong>。布尔型只能是true或者fals。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">if ( whether &amp;&amp; !done )</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">6、默认的浮点类型是双精度（double），要想要一个float必须在浮点数后面加F或者f。如：float pi = 3.14;是错误的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;7、默认的整数类型是int型，要想使用长整型可在后面加&ldquo;l&rdquo;或&ldquo;L&rdquo;，如：1000L。（小写l容易被误认为1，不推荐用）</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;8、float可以精确到7位有效数字，第8位的数字是第9位数字四舍五入上取得的；double可以精确到16位有效数字，第17位的数字是第18位数字四舍五入上取得的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;9、如果要求精确的答案，请不要使用float和double，尤其是对货币计算尤为不适合，选择使用BigDecimal.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">10、Java为所有的成员变量提供了默认初始化：byte、short、 int、long--0 &nbsp;float--0.0f double--0.0 &nbsp;boolean--false &nbsp;char--\'\"u0000\'，特别地对象类型的引用全被初始化为null。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;11、基本类型之间的转化。Java的类型检查很严格，从低精度转换到高精度是无须显式转换的，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">double d = 12.5;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">float f = (int) d; //结果不是13，而是12！</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">浮点型转化为整型时，不进行四舍五入，直接截断小数点后面的数。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;12、</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">int和long运算，结果是long，整型和浮点型运算结果是浮点型。特殊的一点是：只要类型比int小（如char、byte、short），那么在运算之前，这些值会自动地转换成int。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">三、字符串</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">1、String中的每个字符都是一个16位的Unicode字符，用Unicode很容易表达丰富的国际化字符集。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">2、判断空字符串。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">if ( s == null || s.length()==0 || s.trim().length()==0)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">3、字符串的比较,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">用a.<strong>compareTo</strong>(b) ==0 或 a.equal(b)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">4、String对象是不变的！可以变化的是String对象的引用。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">String的不变性的机制显然会在String常量内有大量的冗余。如：\"1\" + \"2\" + \"3\" +......+ \"n\" 产生了n+(n+1)个String对象！因此Java为了更有效地使用内存，JVM留出一块特殊的内存区域，被称为&ldquo;String常量池&rdquo;。当编译器遇见String常量的时候，它检查该池内是否已经存在相同的String常量。如果找到，就把新常量的引用指向现有的String，不创建任何新的String常量对象。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">为连接n个字符串使用字符串连接操作时，要消耗的时间是n的平方级！因为每两个字符串连接，它们的内容都要被复制。因此在处理大量的字符串连接时，而且要求性能时，不要用String，StringBuffer是更好的选择。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">5、StringBuffer类。StringBuffer类是可变的，不会在字符串常量池中，而是在堆中，不会留下一大堆无用的对象。而且它可将字符串缓冲区安全地用于多个线程。每个StringBuffer对象都有一定的容量。只要StringBuffer对象所包含的字符序列的长度没有超出此容量，就无需分配新的内部缓冲区数组。如果内部缓冲区溢出，则此容量自动增大。这个固定的容量是16个字符。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">StringBuffer sb = new StringBuffer(); &nbsp;//初始容量16 个字符 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">sb.append(\"12345678901234567\"); //17个字符，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;System.out.println(sb.capacity()); //字符串缓冲区的容量是34</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">6、StringBuilder类。 从J2SE 5.0 提供了StringBuilder类，它和StringBuffer类是孪生兄弟。它存在的价值在于：对字符串操作的效率更高。不足的是线程安全无法保证，不保证同步。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">单个线程的时候使用StringBuilder类，以提高效率，而且它的API和StringBuffer兼容，不需要额外的学习成本，物美价廉。多线程时使用StringBuffer，以保证安全。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">四、</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">数组</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">1、数组不是集合，它只能保存同种类型的多个原始类型或者对象的引用。数组保存的仅仅是对象的引用，而不是对象本身。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">2、数组本身就是对象，Java中对象是在堆中的，因此数组无论保存原始类型还是其他对象类型，数组对象本身是在堆中的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">3、原始类型数组元素的默认值。对于原始类型数组，在用new构造完成而没有初始化时，JVM自动对其进行初始化。默认值：byte、short、 int、long--0 &nbsp;float--0.0f double--0.0 &nbsp;boolean--false &nbsp;char--\'\"u0000\'。（无论该数组是成员变量还是局部变量）</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">对象类型数组中的引用被默认初始化为null。如：Car[] myCar = new Car[10]; 相当于从myCar[0]到myCar[9]都这样被自动初始化为myCar[i] = null;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">4、数组索引的范围。数组中各个元素的索引是从0开始的，到length-1。 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">5、多维数组的构造。float[][] ratings = new float[9][]; 第一维的长度必须给出，其余的可以不写。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">6、数组声明的两种形式：一、int[] arr; 二、int arr[];&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">在数组构造的时候必须指定长度, &nbsp;int[] x = new int[100]; int[] aa = new int[] {3,4,5};</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">7、与数组相关的函数：System.arraycopy(Object src,int srcPos,Object dest,int destPos,int length), Array.sort().</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">五、程序控制流程</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">1、if条件语句: &nbsp;<strong>if</strong>...<strong>else</strong>...&nbsp;可简写为：变量 = 布尔表达式? 语句1:语句2;&nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>if</strong>...<strong>else if</strong>...<strong>else</strong>...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">2、switch选择语句: <strong>switch</strong>(表达式)&nbsp;{&nbsp;<strong>case</strong> 取值1:&nbsp; &nbsp;语句块1;&nbsp;<strong>break</strong>; &nbsp;<strong>default</strong>:&nbsp;语句块n+1;&nbsp;}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">3、while循环语句: &nbsp;<strong>while</strong>(条件表达式)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">{&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">执行语句</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">4、do while循环语句: &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>do</strong>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">{&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">执行语句</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">} <strong>while</strong>(条件表达式)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">5、for循环语句:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>for</strong>(初始化表达式;循环条件表达式;循环后操作表达式)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">{</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">执行语句</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">6、增强for循环:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>for</strong> (循环变量类型 循环变量名称: 要被遍历的对象)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">{</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;执行语句</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">7、<strong>break</strong>与<strong>continue</strong>语句</span></p>', '甘剑平', '', '', '', '3', 'zh_CN', '', 'manager', 'manager', '2012-09-15 20:53:47', '2012-09-15 22:08:10', '0');
INSERT INTO cm_article VALUES ('4028d98139c7796a0139ca8c8a600317', 'Java04', 'Java面向对象', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">一、面向对象概念</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">1、</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">封装性</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">是面向对象的根源和最根本的属性。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">2、<strong>类</strong>是对某一类事物的描述，是抽象的、概念上的定义；<strong>对象</strong>（Object）是类（Class）的一个实例（Instance）。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">二、<strong>类</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>/**</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; * &nbsp;定义类就是定义类的属性与行为（方法）</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; * 访问控制修饰符共有四个：public、protected、default、private。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; */ &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">public&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">abstract&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;\">class</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Parent</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;{</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">//静态常量</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">，只能赋以一次值。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; private <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">static final</span> int IP;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">静态变量,</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">在类被被载入时创建,</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">访问该变量不需要产生类的实例对象。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">protected <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>static</strong></span> Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(BaseModel.class);&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>类的封装</strong>：将类的成员变量声明为private，再通过public方法来对这个变量进行访问。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">private</span>&nbsp;String str;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">构造函数的作用：为类的成员变量完成初始化工作。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">public Parent(String name) {&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; this.name=name;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;//对静态常量赋值</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">static</span> {</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IP =&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">BytesUtil.toInt(InetAddress.getLocalHost().getAddress());</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">基本类型的变量作为实参传递，传递的是该数据的值本身，变量并不会改变。而引用类型(类，String类除外)则会变</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; public void m<strong>ethod</strong>(String str1, User user) {</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;String str = \"parent\";&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;String name = str;//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">方法中有与类的成员变量同名的局部变量，对这个变量名的访问是局部变量，而不是成员变量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">public void <strong>method</strong>(double d){</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;//<strong>方法的重载</strong>是在编译时刻就决定调用哪个方法了，和重写不同。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">public</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;\">final</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">String <strong>finalMethod</strong>(Date date) {</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //该方法不能被重写</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; public String getStr() {</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return this.str;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><span><span><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;public&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">finalize() {</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">在对象已变成垃圾即将从内存中释放前调用, &nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">System.gc</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">()可以强制启动垃圾回收器来回收垃圾。</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;public <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">static</span> void main (String[] args) {</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">//</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">在<strong>静态方法</strong>里只能直接调用同类中的其他静态成员（变量和方法）。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;静态方法不能被覆盖。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\"><strong>public</strong> <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">class</span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Child</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">extends</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Parent&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">{&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">public Child(String name) { //</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">构造函数的作用：为类的成员变量完成初始化工作。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; super(name);</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">public String <strong>method</strong>(String str1, User user) {</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;//<strong>重写</strong>父类方法，抽象方法是必须被重新的方法，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">重写方法可以实现<strong>多态</strong>，用父类的引用来操纵子类对象。重写对应运行时</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">}</span></p>', '甘剑平', '', '', '', '4', 'zh_CN', '', 'manager', 'manager', '2012-09-15 23:29:31', '2012-09-16 01:09:31', '0');
